    uptitle="— Our Services"
    title="Welcome to Eagle Aircraft Flight Academy"
    subtitle="Eagle Aircraft delivers FAA-approved, structured flight training backed by 40+ years of excellence. With expert instructors and real-world flying, we prepare you to become a confident, skilled, safety-driven pilot."
